43:14.182 --> 43:16.314
Oh, John, just so you know,
since you're new here,

43:16.316 --> 43:17.249
I'm a poet.

43:17.251 --> 43:19.318
A street poet.

43:19.320 --> 43:21.287
And a gay activist.

43:21.289 --> 43:23.622
So, I was
at the Pendleton Round-Up,

43:23.624 --> 43:27.193
and I took the opportunity
to read one of my poems,

43:27.195 --> 43:30.829
which has in it a number
of references to young cocks.

43:30.831 --> 43:32.830
This is it.

43:32.832 --> 43:35.367
"Hot...

43:35.369 --> 43:37.303
in the summer sun.

43:37.305 --> 43:41.273
Working all day, hustling hay.

43:41.275 --> 43:43.943
It's getting harder

43:43.945 --> 43:46.312
and harder

43:46.314 --> 43:48.247
