49:46.340 --> 49:48.774
There's one
in my right shirt pocket here.

49:48.776 --> 49:51.044
The jacket here. Go get it.
It's another quart.

50:04.825 --> 50:06.291
Okay, great.

50:06.293 --> 50:08.026
