Mr. Katz will see you.

50:10.597 --> 50:12.266
Oh, thank you.

50:19.974 --> 50:21.640
Afternoon.

50:21.642 --> 50:23.041
Good afternoon.

50:23.043 --> 50:25.644
Thanks so much for taking
the time to see me.

50:25.646 --> 50:27.312
Not at all.

50:27.314 --> 50:29.981
- What can I do for you?
- My name is John Callahan.

50:29.983 --> 50:33.651
I was born in 1950 at the old
Saint Vincent's Hospital.

50:33.653 --> 50:36.021
I know three things
about my real mother:

50:36.023 --> 50:38.689
she was Irish-American,
she had red hair,

50:38.691 --> 50:40.892
- she was a school teacher.
- Mm-hmm.

50:40.894 --> 50:43.361
Oh, yeah.
And she didn't want me.

50:43.363 --> 50:45.329
So, four things.

50:45.331 --> 50:47.064
Anyway, I was hoping
you could help me find her.

50:47.066 --> 50:52.771
I-I made this sketch of what
I think she might look like.

50:52.773 --> 50:55.309
Maybe it'll help you out.

50:59.046 --> 51:00.711
It's very nice.

51:00.713 --> 51:02.314
Callahan.

51:02.316 --> 51:03.814
Yeah, John.

51:03.816 --> 51:06.651
Old Saint Vincent's Hospital.

51:06.653 --> 51:08.922
Well... let's see.

51:17.097 --> 51:18.829
That's really my file?

51:18.831 --> 51:20.097
All right. This is the one.

51:20.099 --> 51:21.700
That's it? Let me look at it.

51:21.702 --> 51:23.838
Yeah, we'll go back over.

51:25.706 --> 51:27.842
All right.

51:34.814 --> 51:36.080
What's it say?

51:36.082 --> 51:38.086
Uh...

51:39.820 --> 51:41.753
Well, Mr. Callahan,
there's little I can do.

51:41.755 --> 51:43.421
Wait. No, you saw something.

51:43.423 --> 51:45.823
- Mr. Callahan. Mr. Callahan.
- What's in there? What'd you...

51:45.825 --> 51:47.358
The state of Oregon has a law.

51:47.360 --> 51:49.727
Forget the state of Oregon,
man. Come on.

51:49.729 --> 51:50.928
Mr. Callahan,
I could lose my job.

51:50.930 --> 51:53.097
- There's just nothing I can do.
- Wait, what does that say?

51:53.099 --> 51:55.800
Is that... is that
"Maggie Lynch"?

51:55.802 --> 51:57.102
- I can't say, Mr....
- Is that her name?

51:57.104 --> 51:59.104
- Maggie Lynch?
- Mr. Callahan, I can't say.

51:59.106 --> 52:00.972
What do you mean you can't say?
It's written down right there.

52:00.974 --> 52:02.340
I just saw it.
Is that her name, Maggie Lynch?

52:02.342 --> 52:05.142
Mr. Callahan, I am not
gonna lose my job.

52:05.144 --> 52:06.812
Screw your job, man.

52:06.814 --> 52:08.345
You've probably been
sitting behind this desk

52:08.347 --> 52:09.780
- for 25 fucking years.
- Mr. Callahan,

52:09.782 --> 52:10.881
- get out.
- You have a miserable life.

52:10.883 --> 52:12.050
