- Get out.

52:12.052 --> 52:14.021
Aw, go fuck yourself.

52:30.503 --> 52:33.140
Maybe it's your battery
or a connection or something.

52:34.108 --> 52:36.207
There you are.

52:36.209 --> 52:38.175
- Could you spare a quarter?
- Yeah.

52:38.177 --> 52:41.113
234...

52:41.115 --> 52:43.217
2459.

