52:52.159 --> 52:54.191
<i>Just a moment.</i>

52:55.461 --> 52:56.794
This is Suzanne.

52:56.796 --> 52:59.700
<i>Hey, Suzanne. It's John.</i>

53:00.767 --> 53:02.399
