53:02.401 --> 53:05.003
- Could somebody come down here to help me?
- <i>John?</i>

53:05.005 --> 53:06.805
John, this is the third time

53:06.807 --> 53:08.173
in a couple of months
this has happened.

53:08.175 --> 53:09.508
You know, we have cutbacks

53:09.510 --> 53:11.209
ever since the
new president came in.

53:11.211 --> 53:13.879
- <i>We have our own problems.</i>
- Oh, please don't start.

53:13.881 --> 53:16.013
