Suzanne...

53:16.015 --> 53:18.850
<i>John, I'm sorry,
I do not make the rules.</i>

53:18.852 --> 53:20.852
What did I do to you?

53:20.854 --> 53:23.120
What did I do
to piss you off so much?!

53:23.122 --> 53:24.990
- Why you got to treat me like this?
- <i>You know,</i>

53:24.992 --> 53:27.091
I hear you're putting a lot
more mileage on that wheelchair

53:27.093 --> 53:28.260
than the average quadriplegic.

53:28.262 --> 53:30.227
Yeah, because
I'm an active worker!

53:30.229 --> 53:32.863
I'm not a fucking
nursing home vegetable!

53:32.865 --> 53:35.100
So I'm just asking for
a little bit of goddamn help!

53:35.102 --> 53:36.901
- Take care, John.
- <i>Suzanne,</i>

53:36.903 --> 53:39.070
please, please,
I fucking beg you.

53:39.072 --> 53:41.506
- I ask for forgiveness!
- Take care of yourself, please.

53:41.508 --> 53:42.843
<i>Please, please!</i>

53:53.586 --> 53:55.519
