the objectives of group

53:55.521 --> 53:58.957
is to provoke a new awareness
to unwanted

53:58.959 --> 54:03.128
or unnecessary emotional
problems that we sit with.

54:03.130 --> 54:04.963
And left unprovoked,

54:04.965 --> 54:07.032
we sit alone
with these problems,

54:07.034 --> 54:10.901
and they can fester into...
drinking habits,

54:10.903 --> 54:13.171
drug habits, gambling.

54:13.173 --> 54:15.573
Other bad habits.

54:15.575 --> 54:17.142
What are "other bad habits"?

54:17.144 --> 54:19.044
I mean, it could be anything.

54:19.046 --> 54:22.613
It could be hoarding,
bank robbing, suicide.

54:22.615 --> 54:24.182
It happens, amiga.

54:24.184 --> 54:25.916
Mike.

54:25.918 --> 54:28.253
Why don't you tell us
your story.

54:28.255 --> 54:30.588
Talk about your employment;
start from the beginning.

54:30.590 --> 54:32.090
What was the name
of the company?

54:32.092 --> 54:33.624
Uh...

54:33.626 --> 54:36.894
Burnside Exploratory
Systems Technology.

54:36.896 --> 54:38.629
And we called it BEST
for short.

54:38.631 --> 54:40.599
I, uh...

54:40.601 --> 54:44.501
had an administrator there
I didn't care for very much.

54:44.503 --> 54:46.271
Once a war going on,
and she didn't care

54:46.273 --> 54:48.173
whether we were winning
or losing when I worked there,

54:48.175 --> 54:49.908
and we were handed
a lot of bullshit.

54:49.910 --> 54:51.609
Slow down, Mike. Y-You...

54:51.611 --> 54:55.046
- "She," meaning your administrator?
- Yeah.

54:55.048 --> 54:56.981
Yeah, and she...

54:56.983 --> 55:01.051
would just keep to herself
up in her cubicle.

55:01.053 --> 55:02.954
Then we'd hear
her prerecorded voice

55:02.956 --> 55:04.655
come over the loudspeaker.

55:04.657 --> 55:08.158
Can you tell us a little bit
about this administrator?

55:08.160 --> 55:10.294
Yeah.
Yeah, well, first the sentry

55:10.296 --> 55:12.963
in our, uh, attack unit was...

55:12.965 --> 55:14.901
Uh, fuck.

55:15.968 --> 55:17.669
I'm sorry, Donnie, can we, uh,

55:17.671 --> 55:19.336
can we talk about
something else?

55:19.338 --> 55:20.638
No.

55:20.640 --> 55:22.173
How did she make you feel?

55:22.175 --> 55:24.209
Well, we were like family.

55:24.211 --> 55:26.912
You know, you spend enough time
with your family, you...

55:26.914 --> 55:29.981
end up wanting to strangle
your mom, you know?

55:29.983 --> 55:31.349
May I ask something?

